headline: Capital One: Preferred Shares Offer Attractive Current Yields And Capital Gain Potential
summary: Capital One has grown in size following the Discover acquisition, with 14% of the balance sheet funded with common equity. Click here to read why COF is a Hold.

headline: STADIUM CHEF SERIES RETURNS WITH EXCEPTIONAL CHEF-DRIVEN CULINARY EXPERIENCE AT NATIONALS PARK, PRESENTED BY CAPITAL ONE, BENEFITING THE JAMES BEARD FOUNDATION
summary: Marquee Development, in partnership with the James Beard Foundation, is thrilled to announce the return of the Stadium Chef Series at Nationals Park. Presented by Capital One and benefiting the James Beard Foundation, this exclusive event will take place in Washington, D.C. on Wednesday, October 29. Building on the success of last year's event at Nationals Park, the series continues to bring unforgettable culinary experiences since its launch in 2022.
